parser-snapshot.name: bison_leak_temp_list
parser-snapshot.input: select s_acctbal, s_name, n_name, p_partkey, p_mfgr, s_address, s_phone, s_comment from part, supplier, partsupp, nation, "Region" where p_partkey = ps_partkey and s_suppkey = ps_suppkey and p_size = 15 and p_type like '%BRASS' and s_nationkey = n_nationkey and n_regionkey = r_regionkey and "r_Name" = 'EUROPE' and ps_supplycost = ( select min(ps_supplycost) from partsupp, supplier, nation, "Region" where p_partkey = ps_partkey and s_suppkey = ps_suppkey and s_nationkey = n_nationkey and n_regionkey = r_regionkey and "r_Name" = 'EUROPE' and ) order by s_acctbal desc, n_name, s_name, p_partkey limit 100
